snippet.title: Densha de GO! 2 3000-bandai - Gameplay Footage (Replay?)
snippet.description:
There is text on the top right that says 自動運転 which means this playthrough was likely a replay. Though I'll be honest it's been so long I can barely even remember.

Keihin-Tōhoku Line: Yokohama → Ueno

Gameplay was recorded in 60FPS, but something happened during the recording that screwed it up.
